title: Warheads
description: Marcia revisits her own painful memories of the violent events that unfolded in her college campus the day Galactus invaded.Starring AnnaSophia Robb as Marcia Hardesty; Seth Barrish as Phil Sheldon; Method Man as Ben Urich.
